<Meta title="References / Tokens Map / Box Shadow" summary="Elevation values. Each level combines an offset, blur, and semantic shadow color." />

# Box shadow tokens map

Elevation values. Each level combines an offset, blur, and semantic shadow color.

\`\`\`ts
import {boxShadow} from "@khanacademy/wonder-blocks-tokens";
\`\`\`

| Token | CSS Variable | Default | Thunderblocks |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| \`boxShadow.low\` | \`--wb-boxShadow-low\` | \`0 2px 2px 0 rgba(33,36,44,0.16)\` | \`0 2px 2px 0 color-mix(in srgb, #252368 20%, transparent)\` |
| \`boxShadow.mid\` | \`--wb-boxShadow-mid\` | \`0 4px 8px 0 rgba(33,36,44,0.16)\` | \`0 4px 8px 0 color-mix(in srgb, #252368 20%, transparent)\` |
| \`boxShadow.high\` | \`--wb-boxShadow-high\` | \`0 8px 16px 0 rgba(33,36,44,0.16)\` | \`0 8px 16px 0 color-mix(in srgb, #252368 20%, transparent)\` |
"
`;

